description:
by AdigitalMan
What is it about? This extends CLOSE ENCOUNTERS OF THE THIRD KIND with all the scenes from the 3 available versions to the most complete edit ever available. 
Not all the deleted scenes were included, only those which fit for quality and plot.


original Film name: Close Encounters of the Third Kind
new film name: Close Encounters of the Third Kind: The Fourth Kind Extended Edition
production studio: Columbia
faneditor: ADigitalMan
date original movie was created: 16. Nov 77
date fanedit was created: 18. Jan 08
original runtime: 135
new runtime: 150
time cut/added: 15 minutes added

Fanedit details: All scenes from all three versions have been assembled into one cut.

Additional information: Presents the complete story from watchable footage.
fanediting time: 3 days

DVD details:
static menu with audio
NTSC 16:9
Dolby Ac-3 surround sound

Persons involved: ADigitalMan

